Package com.example.meditrackr.adapters.careprovider

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PatientAdapter
    This class displays information about all of the patients that a Care Provider is assigned to in a recycler view (a type of list view).
    PatientAdapter.ViewHolder
    This class puts information about each patient into its own view so we won't display information from one patient as another.
    ProblemAdapter
    This class displays all of the problems of a patient selected from a previous page (using the PatientAdapter) in a recycler view.
    ProblemAdapter.ViewHolder
    This class puts information about each problem into its own view so we won't display information from one problem as another.
    RecordAdapter
    This class displays all of the records of a problem selected from a previous page (using the problem adapter) in a recycler view.
    RecordAdapter.ViewHolder
    This class uses viewHolder to put information about each record into its own view so we won't display information from one record as another.
